<h2>Vagrant Setup</h2>

<h3>Grab the latest <a href="http://downloads.vagrantup.com/">here</a></h3>

<h3>Install it</h3>

<h3>Thats it</h3>

<h2>Adding Boxes</h2>

<p>When you add a box to your local puter it downloads the VM image to your home dir like so:</p>

